ystem, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">Anemia, thalassemia, and other hemoglobinopathies</span></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 32.0298%;" data-mce-style="width: 32.0298%;"><strong>MCV</strong></td><td style="width: 32.0298%;" data-mce-style="width: 32.0298%;">Macrocytic anemia, liver disease</td><td style="width: 32.0298%;" data-mce-style="width: 32.0298%;">Microcytic anemia</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 32.0298%;" data-mce-style="width: 32.0298%;"><strong>WBC</strong></td><td style="width: 32.0298%;" data-mce-style="width: 32.0298%;">Acute stress, infection, malignancies</td><td style="width: 32.0298%;" data-mce-style="width: 32.0298%;">Sepsis, marrow hypoplasia</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 32.0298%;" data-mce-style="width: 32.0298%;"><strong>Platelets</strong></td><td style="width: 32.0298%;" data-mce-style="width: 32.0298%;">Risk of thrombosis</td><td style="width: 32.0298%;" data-mce-style="width: 32.0298%;">Risk of bleeding</td></tr></tbody></table><p><br></p></div>
